text: Our own <@U03FJQPSC0Y> and <@U021CFGT73K> are hosting an education session to showcase the true power of extensibility on HubSpot on *September 8th at 11 AM EST.* Be sure to reserve a spot to this one in the INBOUND molbile app, registration is limited and this one's going to fill up fast! The session is called "Growing Better with Powerful CRM Extensibility" This is a great session for customers and developers alike - we think you'll walk away pretty inspired!

If you're at Partner Day today, don't forget to get there on time for a forward-looking keynote about the HubSpot developer ecosystem, led by <@U04DYGVLJPP>,our SVP of Product and Partnerships, and <@U020R53T6CT>, VP and GM Worldwide Solutions Partner Ecosystem. The event kicks off at 1 PM EST!
